data.description: Looking for land close to town.  This may be the one for you.  This 1.9 +/- acres has easy access and is ready to build.  See attached septic design.  Corners are marked.  Listing sign is on East line by access easement on map, walk North to first corner.  Lightly treed.  Power is available/located at edge of outbuilding at 2515 Willa.  4 party well, last water hook up available to well is in gravel marked with white paint.  Bring your plans and builder to see this great property.
